en_987597_0	Brigadier W.B.S.M Abeysekara assumed office as the 12th Director of the Directorate of Rehabilitation on Wednesday (4) in his office at the Hekitta, Wattala.
en_987597_1	He symbolized the acceptance of office by leaving his signature for an official document amid religious observances.
en_987597_2	Senior officers including Commandants of Ranaviru Sevana & Mihindu Seth Medura (MSM), Deputy Director Rehabilitation, staff Officers and Other Ranks were present at the office.
